data.description: Welcome home! You will love the 2 story entry with large Arched Windows and tons of natural light. Beautiful Kitchen with granite, pendant lights  & large island. Living Room and Den share a 2 sided Fireplace. Recent laminate flooring and paint. Study/Bedroom downstairs with easy access to full bathroom w/shower. Upstairs offers Large Primary Bedroom en-suite Bath garden tub, separate shower, double sinks and walk in closet. There are 2 additional good size bedrooms, bathroom w/double sinks and game room. Good size back yard located in a culdesac. You will not be disappointed.
